---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="main-footer">
  <div class="footer-container">
    <div class="footer-main-row">
      
      <div class="footer-left">
        <a href="/" class="footer-logo">DataSecureTools<span class="dot">.</span></a>
        <p class="mission-text">
          Açık kaynak vizyonuyla, dijital güvenliği herkes için erişilebilir kılmak adına bu araçları **tamamen ücretsiz** sunuyoruz. 
          Abonelik veya gizli ücretler olmadan, interneti daha şeffaf ve güvenli hale getirmeyi amaçlayan bir topluluk projesidir.
        </p>
        <nav class="legal-links">
          <a href="/about">Hakkımızda</a>
          <a href="/privacy">Gizlilik Politikası</a>
          <a href="/terms">Hizmet Şartları</a>
          <a href="/contact">İletişim</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer-right">
        <span class="tools-title">Popüler Araçlar</span>
        <div class="tools-grid">
          <div class="tools-col">
            <a href="/tools/ip-lookup">IP Analizi</a>
            <a href="/tools/security-auditor">Güvenlik Denetimi</a>
            <a href="/tools/seo-analyzer">SEO Denetleyici</a>
            <a href="/tools/port-scanner">Port Tarayıcı</a>
            <a href="/api">API Inspector</a>
          </div>
          <div class="tools-col">
            <a href="/tools/tech-stack-spy">Tech Stack Spy</a>
            <a href="/tools/domain-trust">Alan Adı Güveni</a>
            <a href="/tools/web-scraper">Web Scraper</a>
            <a href="/tools/speed-test">Hız Testi</a>
            <a href="/tools/robots-txt">Robots.txt Gen</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <div class="copyright-area">
        <span class="copyright-text">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} DataSecureTools. All rights reserved.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-motto">Building Secure & Automated Digital Futures</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .main-footer {
    padding: 80px 20px 40px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
  }
  .footer-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .footer-main-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .footer-left {
    flex: 1.2;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .dot { color: #4f46e5; }
  .mission-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    max-width: 450px;
  }
  .mission-text strong { color: #4f46e5; }
  
  .legal-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .legal-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .legal-links a:hover { color: #4f46e5; }

  .footer-right {
    flex: 1.5;
  }
  .tools-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }
  .tools-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .tools-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    flex: 1;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .tools-col a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .tools-col a:hover {
    color: #4f46e5;
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid #f8fafc;
    padding-top: 30px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .copyright-text {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }
  .footer-motto {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .footer-main-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 50px; }
  }
</style>